LINDAT/CLARIN Common Theme
==========================

wiki: <https://redmine.ms.mff.cuni.cz/projects/lindat-common/wiki>

Development
-----------

To be able to use `index.htm` and see the current `header.htm` and `footer.htm` you will have to run inside a http server.

* Python:

        python -m SimpleHTTPServer 8000

* Node.js:

        $ npm install -g http-server   # install dependency
        $ http-server -p 8000

* PHP >= 5.4

        php -S 127.0.0.1:8000


Note: clone the repository recursively
git clone --recursive https://github.com/ufal/lindat-repository.git

For already cloned repositories:
git submodule update --init --recursive
